OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome cloud
OL,6,Fbreaks may develop from the north, and
OL,7,Fturning chilly where these occur.
OL,8,FOtherwise, largely cloudy, with hill
OL,9,Ffog and the odd spot of drizzle. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FGradually turning brighter
OL,13,Ffrom the north and mostly dry,
OL,14,Falthough isolated showers are still
OL,15,Fpossible. Winds remaining generally
OL,16,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
