OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,7,Fshowers each day, although perhaps
OL,8,Fmore likely on Tuesday. Turning
OL,9,Fcooler, with overnight rural frost
OL,10,Fpossible in sheltered spots. Winds
OL,11,Fmostly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
